title: WORD DOC WELTGESCHICHTE ALTERTUM
description:
PLEASE NOTE: I HAVE PREPARED THIS FOR STUDENTS

             IN A SUPER-ECONOMIC FORMAT

             (printing a page costs usually 10 eurocents)





YOU CAN EDIT THE WORD DOCUMENT ACCORDING TO YOUR TASTE.



---------------------------------------------------------


This are the books dealing with the (mediterranean) ancient history ,

out of the Fischer Weltgeschichte.

This well known collection was published in 1965-1974 , being second only to the cambridge history in quality but far , far more read due to the economic edition of the collection.



Usually this books are read in english , spanish , french.

Here you have the original german text if you are interested in either the text itself or simply you are learning german and need good texts to study , print and analyze the verbs , subordinate phrases etc.


About 1000 pages , or being more realistic about six months of hard work.


The authors: Bengtson , Grimal , Fergus Millar , Franz G. Maier.
